  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Use Manrope for both headings and body font. Load from Google Fonts in index.css.",
    "Do NOT use pure white background globally, use the #FDFCF8 (sand-50) or #F5F5F0 (stone) for dashboard backgrounds to reduce eye strain, and plain white #FFFFFF for cards.",
    "All interactive elements must have data-testid attributes for testing.",
    "Dashboard layout must have a sticky sidebar navigation and a top header with glassmorphism.",
    "Implement clear visual hierarchies using the tailwind color variables provided.",
    "Incorporate Shadcn components (tables, calendars, inputs) but override their default border and radius styles to match these guidelines.",
    "Do NOT use placeholder text or dummy image URLs. ALWAYS use the images provided in media_urls."
  ]
}